Gertrude Hesser, appellee, v. Chicago City Railway Company et al., appellants.Gen. No. 33,877.Heard in the third division of this court for the first district at the October term, 1929.

Friend, J., not participating.

Opinion filed October 29, 1930.Brown, Fox & Blumberg, for appellants; Frank L. Kriete, John E. Kehoe, Charles LeRoy Brown and James L. Coleman, of counsel. Murphy O. Tate, for appellee. Mr. Justice Hebei

delivered the opinion of the court.
